<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-29 14:54 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4031 &Cx1f; tab-z
r p BC-`PRALINE'-GOP-750&AMP;add     11-29 1987
