<HEADLINE>
OXFAM: WHAT WTO MEANS TO THE WORLD'S POOR  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Commentary Editors...TIMELY for WTO summit, Seattle)   (This TIMELY 925-word ``separate-buy'' commentary is from the
International Herald Tribune.)  
  
