<P>
   RELIGION-JONES-COLUMN &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ The Rev. Jerry Falwell is getting even closer to the
national Southern Baptist Convention. Last week, Liberty
University, a 9,400-student liberal arts school in Lynchburg, Va.,
that Falwell founded, became officially affiliated with the
Southern Baptist Convention. It is no surprise. By JIM JONES. Story
has moved in ``l'' lifestyle category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
