<P>
   ECOMMERCE _ Early reports show ecommerce is following the lead
of its brick and mortar sister and is having a burst in sales for
the holiday season and well on its way to meeting predicted sales
of $8 billion for the season. Amazon.com which previously reported
its best day ever prior to the beginning of the holiday retail
season Nov. 26, had its biggest day on Friday, Nov. 26. (Katz,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 14.
</P>
<P>
   DELTA-UNION _ Rank-and-file votes are counted today on a pay
rate agreement between Delta and its pilot union covering two new
airplanes, the Boeing 777 and 767-400. Approval is needed if Delta
is to proceed with its plans to add the new widebodies to its
fleet. (Thurston, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 12.
</P>
