<TEXT>
<P>
   The always cheery Wired magazine has compiled a list of 100
things that should be put in the dump file before they ``cross the
glittering rainbow bridge to the third you-know-what.'' Some
selections:
</P>
<P>
   :-) and all its brethren emoticons, recovered memory syndrome,
 &UR; Courtney Love &LR; , white stretch limos, ``What's Sexy Now!,''
spinning (not fibers), forwarded e-mail jokes, zero tolerance,
trilogies,  &UR; David Letterman &LR; .
